Invocation Name: golden girls trivia
des:
Hey, Dorothy... it's me, Stan! Are you ready to test your knowledge of all things Golden Girls? From Miami to St. Olaf; from Sicily to Shady Pines — Golden Girls Trivia has you covered!

∙ The perfect family-friendly trivia game for all fans of The Golden Girls.
∙ Over 70 questions with new questions added weekly!
∙ Grab a slice of cheesecake and head out to the lanai — Golden Girls Trivia awaits!

Thank you for being a friend!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
